Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:33.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}人类动物园，我不敢相信居然还存在\N{\fnArial\fs32}The Human Zoo. I can't believe it still exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸肯定在里面\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad's got to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只要找到他并将他救出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just have to find him and bust him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:47.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那些宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs32}Those Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:49.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶守卫\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:51.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:53.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好像我们能大摇大摆的走进去\N{\fnArial\fs32}Like we could just waltz up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:55.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一个无主的珍珠，一个融合体，\N{\fnArial\fs32}as an ownerless Pearl, a Fusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}和-和，你\N{\fnArial\fs32}and -- and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:01.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只需要伪装，我就叫“艾斯呆板·宇宙老爹”\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just need disguises. I'll be Esteban Universedad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，你的名字并没有用\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, it doesn't matter what your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们太显眼了\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're all going to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不会\N{\fnArial\fs32}We won't stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}只要我们的表现与本来的身份一致的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}if we play the roles we were made for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:13.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}红宝石！蓝宝石！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ruby! Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，各位，听她的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay everybody, hear her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:20.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}今天，我，作为蓝宝石，正在执行公务，伴随我的有红宝石护卫...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Today, I'm a Sapphire traveling with my Ruby guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:23.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有我个人的珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs32}And my personal Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯-哼！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}艾斯呆板，我将你作为献给动物园的大礼\N{\fnArial\fs32}Esteban, I've brought you as an offering for the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}“可怜的艾斯呆板啊！”\N{\fnArial\fs32}{\i1}Pobrecito Esteban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，我呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你作为额外打手陪同我\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're accompanying me as extra muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}像她们那种？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Muscle like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没错\N{\fnArial\fs32}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我从没看见过其他紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs32}But I've never even seen another Amethyst before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那我做什么？如果我说错话了呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What do I do? What if I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}看着办吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你too young，我们长者\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're new and we're rusty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:49.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只用坚持到找到格雷格就行\N{\fnArial\fs32}but we just have to sell this long enough to find Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这真的管用吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:52.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不\N{\fnArial\fs32}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们得呆在一起，直截了当\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just stick together, play it straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让我们改变未来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们永远不可能关住我的，你们这群石头蛋！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You'll never cage me, ya rock heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}说明来意\N{\fnArial\fs32}State your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我是来完成动物园的货运任务的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm here to make a delivery to the Human Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坏消息-人类动物园关闭了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Bad news -- the Human Zoo shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:25.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也就是意味着我们不得不把你直接扔进太空\N{\fnArial\fs32}which means we'll just have to throw you into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哈！看，他居然信了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ha! Look. It believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:34.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们在干吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没什么，霍利蓝玛瑙\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nothing, Holly Blue Agate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}为什么你不告诉我\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why didn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝宝石来这里了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}there was a Sapphire here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你对她说了什么不敬的话吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What have you miscreants been saying to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没有，长官\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nothing, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你一定要见谅啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}You'll have to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他们来自地球\N{\fnArial\fs32}They're from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}咳！道歉\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ahem! Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}请原谅我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗷！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}请原谅我们，您的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}Forgive us, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没必要再揪着旧事不放\N{\fnArial\fs32}No use dwelling on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我为收藏集合带来了一个新的人类\N{\fnArial\fs32}I've brought a new human for the collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这多么新奇啊-\N{\fnArial\fs32}How unprecedented --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一千年来什么都出现\N{\fnArial\fs32}nothing for millennia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而现在突然两个人类接踵而至！\N{\fnArial\fs32}and then two humans back-to-back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许，这样最好吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, it's probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}第一个的状态...并不好\N{\fnArial\fs32}That first one wasn't in the...best condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸！那是他！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:18.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘘！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，人类无尽无休的叫唤！他在叫唤什么啊？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, they're incessant barking! What is it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}-另一个也很吵\N{\fnArial\fs32}- The other one was loud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且还在不停挣扎\N{\fnArial\fs32}And all that thrashing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:32.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很确定蓝钻石愿意亲自表达谢意\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sure Blue Diamond will want to thank you personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但你刚好错过她了\N{\fnArial\fs32}but you just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶，带这个人类去-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst, take this human to the --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}有件事，我们走了那么远\N{\fnArial\fs32}The thing is we've traveled so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果就这么离开实在是可惜\N{\fnArial\fs32}and it would be a shame to leave so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许你能带我们参观一下设施？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Perhaps you'd grant us a tour of the facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我非常荣幸\N{\fnArial\fs32}I would be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}来这里，您伟大的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right this way, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶得留在这里看门\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethysts are to stay and guard the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，但...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}大门\N{\fnArial\fs32}The door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你的珍珠总是与您肩并肩行走吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Does your Pearl always walk next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我在这就好\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll just be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯，很贫嘛\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hmm. Chatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:17.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}此设施原来属于粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}This facility originally belonged to Pink Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}收留并任用本来毫无用处的石英们\N{\fnArial\fs32}and houses and staffs the otherwise useless Quartzes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那些石英制造于她的殖民地\N{\fnArial\fs32}she produced on what was her colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但蓝钻石与她值得信赖的玛瑙-\N{\fnArial\fs32}But Blue Diamond and her trusted Agate --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也就是我-\N{\fnArial\fs32}that's me --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}自第二代的曙光后一直在维护这个地方\N{\fnArial\fs32}have been maintaining this place since the dawn of Era 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是她要做什么，还是我要先说什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Is she going to do it, or should I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠，门\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl, the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯？噢！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好，好\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:43.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你对她真是有耐心啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}You are so patient with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你是如何做到的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}作为蓝宝石，我知道这肯定会发生的\N{\fnArial\fs32}As a Sapphire, I know it will happen eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就这样吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:02.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坚持一下\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}跟上啊，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs32}Do keep up, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这个设施的下半部分\N{\fnArial\fs32}The bottom half of this structure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}完全关注于物种保存\N{\fnArial\fs32}is devoted entirely to specimen containment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}显然，人类不愿意被拘禁\N{\fnArial\fs32}Apparently, humans don't take well to captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但只要你了解他们的需求\N{\fnArial\fs32}But once you understand their needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他们很容易控制\N{\fnArial\fs32}they're easy to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:25.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这真是个悲剧-粉钻在宇宙中的存在\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's tragic that Pink Diamond's existence in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}居然如此有限\N{\fnArial\fs32}ended up being so finite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但蓝钻的表现是如此无私，\N{\fnArial\fs32}But what a selfless act for Blue Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}愿意站出来花费自己的时间与精力\N{\fnArial\fs32}to step forward and spend her own time and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}保存这个地方-只为纪念粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}preserving this place in Pink Diamond's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是蓝钻石仁慈与友爱\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's a real testament to Blue Diamond's merciful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真正的纪念碑，你不觉得吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}and giving nature, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，当然\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坚持住，红宝石，我们的角色，记得吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hold it together, Ruby. Our roles, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42\pos(640,80)\c&HFABDA0&}然后走这里，是健康保留分区\N{\fnArial\fs32}And pass this way, the health reservation sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一定要“艾斯呆板”住啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Gotta Esteban it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而这里，显然，是人类处理滑槽\N{\fnArial\fs32}And here, of course, is the human disposal chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如-如何进入动物园？\N{\fnArial\fs32}H-How do get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，又是那滑稽的噪音\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, there it goes again with its hilarious noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，你是如何进入动物园的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, how do you get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:03.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}非常好的问题，您伟大的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}Excellent question, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}在一些特别情况下\N{\fnArial\fs32}On the rare occasion that we would need
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们进入收容区域\N{\fnArial\fs32}to enter the containment area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}要通过这个维护大门\N{\fnArial\fs32}we would do so via this service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，这个门是我们找到爸爸的关键\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad. That door's how we get to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只需要分散一下注意力\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just need to come up with a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:14.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}作为单向接入点，这里并没有发生逃脱的可能性\N{\fnArial\fs32}As one-way access point, there are no risks of an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}实际上，只有一次这里被用于一个人类-\N{\fnArial\fs32}In fact, it's only been used once for a human --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爆炸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:28.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我刚想起来我忘了关掉引力引擎了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just remembered I left the gravity engine idling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起，蓝宝石，我真是健忘和廉价啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, my Sapphire, I'm so forgetful and disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:33.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}...是一个我预见到的事件\N{\fnArial\fs32}...a foreseen turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是的，它将会过热并爆炸\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, it is going to overheat and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}破坏会非常巨大\N{\fnArial\fs32}The damage will be massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我的言辞啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}My word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不知道为什么有人会将宇宙飞船托付给红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't know why anyone trusts Rubies with those ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这就是后果\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果我们抓紧，我们能关掉引擎\N{\fnArial\fs32}If we hurry, we can disable the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}避免任何破坏\N{\fnArial\fs32}before any damage is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我应该只要五分钟\N{\fnArial\fs32}I should only take five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以每个人要做到行为规矩\N{\fnArial\fs32}so everyone be on your best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:00.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}噢！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}来这里，您的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}This way, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}虽然，我确定你不需要我的指引\N{\fnArial\fs32}Although, I'm sure you don't need my guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:09.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我才不信\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can't believe all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝宝石有那么仁慈！\N{\fnArial\fs32}about Blue Diamond being merciful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她会粉碎宝石啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She's a shatterer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她对蓝宝石大喊大叫！她憎恨融合！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She yelled at Sapphire! She hates Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有爱！\N{\fnArial\fs32}And love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道，红宝石，但我们并没有多少时间了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I know, Ruby, but we don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们得打开这道门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We have to open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好，好\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠，开门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当然，我还会做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Of course. What else am I good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这个和其他的不一样\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's different than the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊哈！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我其实根本理解不了这个\N{\fnArial\fs32}I actually can't figure this out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但珍珠，你是团队里的骇客\N{\fnArial\fs32}But Pearl, you're our hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们没那么多时间！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，帮我打开门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, help me open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有，珍珠，骇得快点！\N{\fnArial\fs32}And Pearl, hack faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很高兴我们马上就回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I am so glad we're almost back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我真的很享受这次行程！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I was really enjoying the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}使得，我能从你的声音里听出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, I can tell by the tone of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}再次感谢你避免了这次危机\N{\fnArial\fs32}Thank you so much again for averting that crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，呃，我确定这有合理的解释-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, well, I'm sure there's a reasonable --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们看到是哪个紫晶做的吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Did you see the Amethyst that did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们可是有客人\N{\fnArial\fs32}Really, we have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}霍利蓝玛瑙-我们有非常重要的消息给你！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Holly Blue Agate, - We have important news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们在这些走廊中不能跑动或喧哗！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We do not run or shout in these hallways!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我对不起，只-只是-\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sorry, i-it's just that --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我怎么听出来你要说什么，\N{\fnArial\fs32}How am I supposed to know what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}像你这样结巴的话？\N{\fnArial\fs32}when you're mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，对不起，霍利蓝玛瑙，只是-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, I'm sorry, Holly Blue Agate, it's just --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝钻石要来这里！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Blue Diamond is on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦 ，我的星星啊！她这就回来了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, my stars! She's back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们两个，注意举止！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You two, best behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}肩膀要平！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Shoulders squared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}头脑专注！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Minds cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}站直了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Backs straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且，蓝钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}And surely, Blue Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}肯定想亲自对您表达谢意\N{\fnArial\fs32}will want to thank you personally
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}非常感谢您的特别货物，您伟大的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}for this special delivery, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是的，我觉得她会的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, I suppose she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么别傻站在这里，你们这群没用的地球土包子，\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well don't just stand there, you useless chunks of earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}做点实事，护送那个人类\N{\fnArial\fs32}make yourself useful and escort that human
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}到同化隔间！\N{\fnArial\fs32}to the assimilation bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但是行程\N{\fnArial\fs32}But the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，您的明晰，你真\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, Your Clarity, you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我们真的必须得做好准备了\N{\fnArial\fs32}But we really must get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们的钻石随时都会到达！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our Diamond will be here at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}放开我，你们这群大号的紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let me go, you bigger Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哈，这些新鲜的人类真是胆肥啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ha. These newer humans are so spunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}进去吧！\N{\fnArial\fs32}In you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:50.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是-\N{\fnArial\fs32}What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:03.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我自己会脱\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}看样子只能光着身子找爸爸了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll just find my dad without pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}腰部裙\N{\fnArial\fs32}Loin cloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，还有什么？你们还想从我这里得到什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay, what else, huh? What else you got for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我现在处于老爸任务的肾上腺素模式\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm on that dad-mission adrenalin rush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}随时准备着对付你们接下来的太空狗屁呢\N{\fnArial\fs32}and ready for whatever space junk you have next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}高科技赶牛棒，人用马掌-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Futuristic cattle prods, human horseshoes --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}随便你，来对付我啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}whatever you got, come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:03.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么-\N{\fnArial\fs32}What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是哪里？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而-而且爸爸在...\N{\fnArial\fs32}A-And where's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这儿？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad?
